<p begin="00:04:36.376" end="00:04:41.348" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">GOT ALL THESE CLEVER LITTLE<br/>THINS WORKED OUT.</span></p>
<p begin="00:04:41.381" end="00:04:44.284" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">YOU HAVE TO DRAW A COUPLE DICKS<br/>ON A PICTURE.</span></p>
