<p begin="00:05:11.044" end="00:05:17.184" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; I BELIEVE WE NEED A NEW<br/>APPROACH, ONE IN WHICH THE</span></p>
<p begin="00:05:17.217" end="00:05:22.356" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">PROVIDERS RETAIN THE RECORDS<br/>WITH  GOVERNMENT ACCESSING</span></p>
