<p begin="00:05:23.056" end="00:05:26.293" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">&gt;&gt; Jon: WHAT? <br/>NOT EVEN THE</span></p>
<p begin="00:05:26.326" end="00:05:29.897" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">GOVERNMENT TRUSTS<br/>THE GOVERNMENT WITH OUR</span></p>
<p begin="00:05:29.930" end="00:05:33.166" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">PRIVATE INFORMATION. SO OUR<br/>DATA WILL APPARENTLY BE</span></p>
<p begin="00:05:33.200" end="00:05:36.970" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">MOVED FROM A BUILDING LIKE THIS<br/>TO A BUILDING LIKE THIS.</span></p>
<p begin="00:05:37.070" end="00:05:41.241" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">[ LAUGHTER ]<br/>PROBLEM SOLVED.</span></p>
